Wrap mode (Repeat or Clamp) of the texture.

Set the texture to clamp at the borders to avoid warping artifacts with TextureWrapMode.Clamp.
Or tile the texture with TextureWrapMode.Repeat.
SA: Texture.wrapMode, [[wiki:class-Texture2D|texture assets]].
CONVERTEXAMPLE
BEGIN EX

	renderer.material.mainTexture.wrapMode = TextureWrapMode.Clamp;
END EX